 ## Standard Definition of Done (Applies to Every Version) 
 
 1. Product acceptance criteria met. 
 2. Unit/integration/E2E coverage complete for changed scope. 
 3. Observability hooks added for new critical paths. 
 4. Security checklist complete for new surface area. 
 5. Runbook updated (deploy, rollback, failure triage). 
 6. ADR updated if architectural decision changed. 
 7. Feature flag and rollout strategy documented. 
 
