 ## Governance Cadence (To Keep the Map Ironclad) 
 
 - **Weekly Architecture Review:** validate boundary discipline and technical debt controls. 
 - **Twice-Weekly Delivery Review:** phase gate status + blocker burn-down. 
 - **Release Readiness Review:** mandatory before each version promotion. 
 - **Incident Feedback Loop:** all incidents produce map/rule updates within 72 hours. 
 
